The '''2011 [[Surinamese Hoofdklasse]] and [[Surinamese Eerste Klasse|Eerste Klasse]] playoffs''' was a home-away aggregate playoff series between the 9th-place Hoofdklasse club of the [[2010&ndash;11 Hoofdklasse (Suriname)|2010&ndash;11]] season, and the winner of the #2 vs. #3 playoff of the [[2010&ndash;11 Surinamese Eerste Klasse|2010&ndash;11]] Eerste Klasse play-off.
