The 2013 version of the [[Syrian Cup]] is the 43rd edition to be played. It is the premier knockout tournament for football teams in Syria. [[Al-Wahda SC Damascus|Al-Wahda]] is the holders.

The winner qualified for the [[2014 AFC Cup]].

16 Teams play a knockout tie, All games will be played over one leg in a neutral Stadium.<ref>http://www.gsf-sport.com/?p=40828</ref>

