{{Infobox football biography |name = Igor Sani |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1986|12|28|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Lisbon]], Portugal |height = {{height|m=1.75}}<ref name = "NFT"/> |position = [[Forward (association football)|Centre forward]]<ref name = "NFT"/> |currentclub = [[GS Loures|Loures]] |clubnumber = |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = 2006–2007 |clubs1 = [[GS Loures|Loures]] |caps1 = |goals1 = |years2 = 2007–2009 |clubs2 = [[GD Igreja Nova|Igreja Nova]] |caps2 = |goals2 = |years3 = 2009–2011 |clubs3 = [[S.C.U. Torreense|Torreense]] |caps3 = |goals3 = |years4 = 2011–2012 |clubs4 = [[S.C. Farense|Farense]] |caps4 = |goals4 = |years5 = 2012–2013 |clubs5 = [[C.D. Fátima|Fátima]] |caps5 = |goals5 = |years6 = 2013–2014 |clubs6 = [[FC Frauenfeld|Frauenfeld]] |caps6 = |goals6 = |years7 = 2014– |clubs7 = [[GS Loures|Loures]] |caps7 = |goals7 = |nationalyears1 = 2014– |nationalteam1 = [[Guinea-Bissau national football team|Guinea-Bissau]] |nationalcaps1 = 2 |nationalgoals1 = 0 |club-update = 18:08, 14 July 2015 (UTC) |ntupdate = 18:08, 14 July 2015 (UTC) }} '''Igor Sani''' (born 28 December 1986) is a Guinea-Bissauan international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for Portuguese team [[GS Loures|Loures]], as a [[Forward (association football)|centre forward]]
==Career== Born in [[Lisbon]], Sani has played club football in Portugal and Switzerland for [[GS Loures|Loures]], [[GD Igreja Nova|Igreja Nova]], [[S.C.U. Torreense|Torreense]], [[S.C. Farense|Farense]], [[C.D. Fátima|Fátima]] and [[FC Frauenfeld|Frauenfeld]].<ref name = "NFT">{{NFT player|pid=56359|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref>
He made his senior international debut for [[Guinea-Bissau national football team|Guinea-Bissau]] in 2014.<ref name = "NFT"/>
