{{Unreferenced|date=July 2013}} {{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Stadio Comunale | image = Stadio Comunale di Chiavari (Tribuna).jpg | image_size = 300px | location = [[Chiavari]], [[Italy]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = 1933 | renovated = | closed = | demolished = | owner = City of [[Chiavari]] | operator = | construction_cost = | architect = | former_names = | tenants = [[Virtus Entella]] | seating_capacity = 5,535 }} '''Stadio Comunale''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Chiavari]], [[Italy]]. It is mainly used for [[association football|football]] matches and hosts the home matches of local Italian Serie C club [[Virtus Entella]]. The stadium has a capacity of 5,535 spectators.
