'''Team Specialized Designs for Women''' (UCI Code: '''TSW''') was an elite women's professional [[road bicycle racing]] [[Cycling team|team]] licensed in [[Switzerland]] that competed in national events (NE), [[UCI rating|UCI-rated]] events (2.HC, 2.1, 2.2, 1.HC, 1.1 and 1.2) and [[UCI Women's Road World Cup]] (WC) events. After operating under various names for seven years, it disbanded at the end of the 2008 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Team Specialized Designs for Women stops|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/team-specialized-designs-for-women-stops|first=Antonio J. |last=Salmerón|newspaper=Cycling News|date=7 October 2008}}</ref>

